================================================================================
ICTU-OpenAgri - Agricultural Technology Platform
================================================================================

Project: ICTU-OpenAgri
Description: An open-source agricultural technology platform providing 
             real-time commodity price tracking, market analysis, and 
             agricultural information services for farmers and stakeholders.
Repository: https://github.com/CuongKenn/ICTU-OpenAgri
Maintainer: CuongKenn

